		<title>11Unemployment</title>
		<content>{UNEMPLOYMENT}                         
 The{Brynmawr-Nantyglo}area is regarded
 as an unemployment blackspot.The      
 unemployment rate is 27%, far higher  
 than the national average.The region  
 was severely hit three years ago by   
 the closure of the Dunlop Semtex      
 factory with the loss of hundreds of  
 jobs. The {Ebbw Vale }unemployment    
 rate is also high at 24% for males and
 12.4% for females giving an average of
 19.2%.                                
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
